  <summary>1/25/2013--Introduced.
Expresses support for the goals and ideals of No Name-Calling Week (an annual week of educational activities to bring attention to name-calling and provide schools with tools to launch an on-going dialogue about ways to eliminate name-calling and bullying in their communities).

Encourages the people of the United States to observe such week with appropriate ceremonies, programs, and activities.</summary>
